    <description>Current state of the scan. Initializing = being set up. Processing = scan running. Paused = engine detected a stall or node cap reached. Completed = scan finished successfully. Failed = unrecoverable error. Cancelled = stopped by user. Do not manually set this field. Ref: ISP-6072</description>
